data.description: Welcome to this stunning one-story David Weekly home located in the highly desirable neighborhood of Indian Springs. This spacious floor plan offers three bedrooms, two bathrooms, and an oversized three-car garage. The new owners will be delighted by the recently remodeled master spa-like bath, as well as the highly energy-efficient solar panels. Additionally, the home features an enormous 27 x 15 covered patio with an outdoor kitchen, perfect for entertaining. The recently installed HVAC system ensures year-round comfort. The versatile 17 x 12 study, currently being used as a second living area, provides endless possibilities for customization. Don't miss the chance to see this incredible home for yourself - schedule an appointment today. You won't be disappointed.
